Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:40.95,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}這份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:46.31,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,350)}也想直接親口告訴你
